<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>À propos</title>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body, html {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        height: 100%;
        color: #1f2937;
        }

        .background {
        position: fixed;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background-image: url("<%= asset_path('background_map.png') %>");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        filter: blur(10px);
        transform: scale(1.05);
        z-index: -2;
        }

        .overlay {
        position: fixed;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(
            rgba(0,0,0,0.4),
            rgba(0,0,0,0.6)
        );
        z-index: -1;
        }

        .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .logo img {
        width: 160px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 5px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2));
        }

        .panel {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 900px;
        padding: 50px;
        border-radius: 20px;

        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px);

        box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
        }

        h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 36px;
        color: white;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .intro {
        text-align: center;
        color: #e5e7eb;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .intro span {
        color: #38bdf8;
        font-weight: 500;
        }

        .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
        }

        .card {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        transition: 0.3s ease;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }

        .card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
        }

        .card h3 {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: white;
        }

        .card p {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #d1d5db;
        line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .back-home {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .home-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 18px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;

        color: white;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);

        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        transition: all 0.25s ease;
        }

        .home-btn:hover {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="background"></div>
  <div class="overlay"></div>

  <div class="container">

    <div class="logo">
      <%= image_tag('logo.png') %>
    </div>

    <div class="back-home">
        <%= link_to "← Retour à l’accueil", root_path, class: "home-btn" %>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">

      <h1>À propos</h1>

      <p class="intro">
        Rendre la recherche de logement <span>simple</span>, <span>rapide</span> et <span>sans stress</span>.
      </p>

      <div class="grid">

        <div class="card">
          <h3>🗺️ Recherche sur carte</h3>
          <p>
            Explorez les logements directement sur une carte interactive.
            Visualisez instantanément les opportunités autour de vous.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>📄 Candidature rapide</h3>
          <p>
            Créez un profil complet et postulez en quelques clics,
            sans ressaisir vos informations à chaque fois.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>📊 Suivi en temps réel</h3>
          <p>
            Suivez vos candidatures et recevez des notifications
            dès qu’un statut change.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>🏡 Côté propriétaires</h3>
          <p>
            Pré-sélectionnez facilement les candidats et consultez
            leurs profils sans appels inutiles.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>📞 Mise en relation</h3>
          <p>
            Contactez uniquement les meilleurs profils pour organiser
            des visites rapidement.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>